<item>
            <title>[LU-5717] Dead lock of nrs_tbf_timer_cb</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5717</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When TBF is enabled, following dead lock problem could be triggered when system is under heavy load.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;Kernel panic - not syncing: Watchdog detected hard LOCKUP on cpu 0&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;4&amp;gt;Pid: 24831, comm: ll_ost_io00_074 Not tainted 2.6.32-431.23.3.el6_lustre.2.5.24.ddn3.x86_64 #1&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;4&amp;gt;Call Trace:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;4&amp;gt; &amp;lt;NMI&amp;gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff8152896c&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ? panic+0xa7/0x16f&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;4&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff81014969&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ? sched_clock+0x9/0x10&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;4&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff810e67fd&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ? watchdog_overflow_callback+0xcd/0xd0&lt;br/&gt;
